{"tid":275943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★［危險］Apple支那員工偷Apple ID網上$10出售！","createTime":"2017-06-08T12:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T09:40:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a56f3e9f86ffb39c30cfe10576ec7b847795fcc","tid":275943,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:03:56.000Z","msg":"蘋果20員工偷Apple ID 牟利半億<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】使用智能手機要加倍小心！浙江溫州蒼南縣公安局近日破獲一宗非法獲取電腦資料系統數據、侵犯公民個人資料案，抓獲廿二名疑犯。當中二十人竟然是蘋果旗下的中國員工，涉嫌偷取Apple ID等客戶個人資料，再在網上轉售圖利，初步查明涉案金額逾五千萬元（人民幣．下同）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據警方調查，該犯罪組織利用蘋果公司內部系統平台，非法查詢蘋果手機關聯的手機號碼、姓名、Apple ID等資料，再將資料以每條十元至一百八十元不等的價格售賣。涉案廿二名疑犯已被刑事拘留，案件正進一步審理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170608/00178_007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170608%2F00178_007.html&d=cDpCooU48CyrVJafXT1IopWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9953308f\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170608/00178_007.html</a>"},{"pid":"366200d072bc249fae917235f4334210580936ce","tid":275943,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"Apple已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05305985d71dda0325fe98f9acfaf377931764ce","tid":275943,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:05:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當中二十人竟然是蘋果旗下的中國員工<br />\n當中二十人竟然是蘋果旗下的中國員工<br />\n當中二十人竟然是蘋果旗下的中國員工<br />\n當中二十人竟然是蘋果旗下的中國員工</span>"},{"pid":"d647b39c6e691d8bd